## The SSRF Hunter's Mindset

### The Golden Rule

> **Any feature that accepts a URL and fetches its content is a potential SSRF vector.**

### Why These Features Are Vulnerable

| Feature Type | Why Vulnerable | Impact |
|--------------|----------------|--------|
| **Image upload by URL** | Server downloads image from user-provided URL | Internal network access |
| **Webhook configs** | Server sends POST requests to user URL | Internal service interaction |
| **PDF generators** | Server renders external content | Metadata access, file read |
| **Link previews** | Server fetches page metadata | Internal page enumeration |
| **Import/export** | Server fetches data from URL | Data exfiltration |

